Title: JET Range Automatic Air Vent Check Valve 3/8 x 1/2"
Description: This JET Range automatic air vent with 3/8 x 1/2" threaded connections is designed with a vacuum break to prevent air locks. A central heating safety device, the air vent releases built up air. As water flows through the system, a float opens or closes the vent depending on the water level. When the system is full the float is pushed to the top, closing the vent until the water level drops.

Title: Altecnic Robocal 15mm Auto Air Vent
Description: Used in heating and air conditioning systems, the Altecnic Robocal automatic air vent works continually to remove air with no need for manual adjustment. Reducing noise and improving the accuracy of control valves along with the performance of heating and cooling equipment, the Robocal releases air as the system is filled with water and automatically isolates, preventing water loss and waste.

Title: Flamco Flexvent Automatic Air Vent 1/2"
Description: The compact Flamco Flexvent 1/2 automatic air vent is a high efficiency unit suitable for use in both heating and air conditioning. Fitted at places where air tends to accumulate, causing corrosion and impacting thermal transfer, the Flexvent collects air, causing a float to drop and open its air release valve. In turn water pressure forces the air out of the system and the float rises again to close the valve. An air cushion is present in the upper part of the unit to protect the valve seat from contamination.

Title: Flamco Flexvent 3/8 Auto Air Vent - 3/8" AAV
Description: The compact Flamco Flexvent automatic air vent, with 3/8" connection, offers highly efficient operation in heating and air conditioning to prevent corrosion and damage and reduce thermal transfer.
